{"tid":1436918,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大提升對香港旅遊警示至「高度警戒」","createTime":"2019-08-09T11:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T11:35:37.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b027b24a6254c30c96b266a7bd6b92b6774ffaaf","tid":1436918,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1473691_1_20190809191047.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1473691_1_20190809191047.jpg&h=d5170922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大政府將對香港的旅遊警示，提升至第二級的「高度警戒」。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大政府表示，自6月9日起，全港多區有多次大規模示威，經批准或未經批准的示威，可能在毫無預警下出現，並可能迅速擴散至附近地方，包括遊客常到的地點，道路及交通可能中斷，商店亦可能突然關門。<br />\n<br />\n公告說，大型集會的安全情況可能迅速變化，或會出現暴力行為，特別是在晚上，警方與示威者衝突，當局使用催淚彈驅散，亦有示威者被持反對意見人士襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n公告呼籲有意到香港的加拿大公民，注意傳媒報道，避免前往示威區或大型集會地點，應聽從香港當局的指示。"},{"pid":"9ce370f3e80f0dad5d6f5634718a2536004a3db6","tid":1436918,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:35:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473691-20190809.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473691-20190809.htm&d=mdS8n1K3gC4RK9SJ0KjOq9UqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=ce11e7fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473691-20190809.htm&h=0329dcde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473691-20190809.htm</a>"}]}